title: The Biggest Solution In The Universe
description:
This torrent contains the complete first season of the podcast called "The Biggest Solution In The Universe" produced by Dick Masterson & Maddox Masterson.

It is smaller brother of the podcast "The Biggest Problem In The Universe" which can be found here: http://thebiggestproblemintheuniverse.com/

I'm only putting this up here as a good Kopimist should, for more information about this show in particular, please visit http://thebiggestproblemintheuniverse.com/the-solutions/ for a chance to also purchase a copy of the episodes to keep.

This torrent also includes all available transcripts as of the upload date
